[Hopefully, these cases are the tail end of the extensive outbreak of measles that affected the northeast of England earlier in the year (2012). A map showing the location of Ormskirk in the county of Lancashire can be accessed at: http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-20510400. - Mod.CP

