[Khairpur District is a district in Sindh province of Pakistan. The district has an area of 15 910 square km and is headquartered at the city of Khairpur. A map of Sindh province showing the location of Khairpur district can be accessed at: http://pamirtours.pk/maps/sindh%20districts%20map.htm. Lack of comprehensive immunisation coverage of rural communities in Pakistan is a continuing problem yet to be overcome. - Mod.CP

